Juventus Appoints Antonio Conte as Coach to Replace Luigi Delneri

-- B y   D a n   L i e f g r e e n
-- 
2011-05-31T14:31:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/juventus-appoints-antonio-conte-as-coach-to-replace-luigi-delneri.html
Juventus Football Club SpA (JUVE)  said it
appointed Antonio Conte as its new coach to replace Luigi
Delneri. The club signed Conte to a two-year contract, Juventus
said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Liefgreen at 
 dliefgreen@bloomberg.net  